bug.description:
I came cross a strange issues only occurred on HuaWei Phone. For phone infomation with this image. <denchmark-link:https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17869361/59587579-26572a00-9118-11e9-8b20-67a14a5c8f08.png></denchmark-link>
At first time run inference no crash, It is always crash at second time. below is crash info. <denchmark-link:https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17869361/59587879-e3498680-9118-11e9-8fe6-bf97e2e2301b.png></denchmark-link>
Below is processed crash info with ndk-stack, but unable to locate in tensorflow source as build tflite from source with no debug symbols and i do not know how to build with debug symbol <denchmark-link:https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17869361/59588620-9a92cd00-911a-11e9-9fb9-ba68baa06f52.png></denchmark-link>
I have tried many methods for building tflite with debug symbol but not successed For example 1„ÄÅ bazel build -c dbg --strip=never --compilation_mode=dbg --per_file_copt=//tensorflow/lite/.*.cc@-g,-O0 //tensorflow/lite:libtensorflowLite.so --crosstool_top=//external:android/crosstool --cpu=armeabi-v7a --host_crosstool_top=@bazel_tools//tools/cpp:toolchain --cxxopt="-std=c++11" with -c dbg --strip=never --compilation_mode=dbg <denchmark-link:https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17869361/59588889-345a7a00-911b-11e9-9424-c3cfcdd87d99.png></denchmark-link>
Crash occurred at 62 line It crashed at second time only on HuaWei Phone. Other phones and ios has no crash. ps:This issue finally crashed at 277 line with below image <denchmark-link:https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17869361/59751454-217aad80-92b3-11e9-8a98-155da7e58c92.png></denchmark-link>
I guess the bias_data address is unavaible <denchmark-link:https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17869361/59751423-10ca3780-92b3-11e9-971c-99ec5e074624.png></denchmark-link>
